---
const brand = "JaiSellers Companies";
const title = "Contact";
const email = "joshuajaisellers@gmail.com";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{title} — {brand}</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Contact JaiSellers Companies. Book consulting, design, or partnership conversations." />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/site.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <header class="topbar">
      <a class="logo" href="/">{brand}</a>
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="/consulting">Consulting (JSC)</a>
        <a href="/design">Design</a>
        <a href="/jsi">JSI</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a class="nav-cta" href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="section">
        <div class="container split">
          <div>
            <p class="kicker">Contact</p>
            <h1>Let’s build something that holds.</h1>
            <p style="margin-top:14px; max-width:70ch;">
              Tell us what you’re building, what’s urgent, and what “done” looks like. We’ll reply with the fastest
              path to stability.
            </p>

            <div class="trust-row" style="margin-top:18px;">
              <span class="pill">Nonprofit formation</span>
              <span class="pill">Grant systems</span>
              <span class="pill">Brand + messaging</span>
              <span class="pill">JSI partnerships</span>
            </div>

            <div class="cta-row" style="margin-top:20px;">
              <a class="btn primary" href={"mailto:" + email + "?subject=JaiSellers%20Companies%20Inquiry"}>Email us</a>
              <a class="btn ghost" href="/consulting">View Consulting</a>
            </div>

            <p class="small" style="margin-top:14px;">
              Email: <a href={"mailto:" + email}>{email}</a><br />
              Mailing: 912 S. Battleground Ave., Kings Mountain, NC 28086
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="callout">
            <h3>What to include</h3>
            <ul class="bullets" style="margin-top:10px;">
              <li>[ORG] name + location</li>
              <li>What you need (formation / grants / brand / ops)</li>
              <li>Deadline (if any)</li>
              <li>Current status (incorporated? EIN? board?)</li>
              <li>Budget range (if known)</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="small" style="margin-top:12px;">
              Want a form instead? Tell me and I’ll add a simple GitHub Pages-safe form option.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="container footer-inner">
        <span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} {brand}</span>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
